text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6de15961-ae3d-4599-9861-36bcd93617e5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70634251-2a48-4695-a197-4b0906e70207\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본 핫 폴더의 색상 값대로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4a7efb71-b981-4392-99fd-00df410ff0a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0dfcb998-55dd-4013-9300-04cbef85f125\" style=\"color:#555555;\">거의 변하지 않고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8fc1bac4-74c0-4dba-aad7-a3452f0c7772\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2666206-8422-4b5e-a92c-0059e382025b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">구현되는 것이 일반화되어</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6d1e2381-edd5-4448-8389-cc6cd562f1aa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f8cbef6-842d-4109-8f0f-e0d7d2505f03\" style=\"color:#555555;\">있기는 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-18600fd8-c726-494b-a428-1167502c5391\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f44523e-f2c4-40e5-8099-a31ea7028042\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6140a130-6f0b-40c7-a23f-24c75695db2d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c7abefe-fd05-4130-9d40-b374fc8b694d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">그러나 인쇄도 결국은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c2acd977-8ebe-437e-acbf-3acaac2ea4c0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70b63bf4-c89e-4db3-b04f-059e15a767cc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">사람의 손을 거쳐</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b1739858-b962-4b58-8c8b-5a5fe4e28acd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6802c08-5734-41e0-951e-96753caef94b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">제작이 되게 되어 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b02ed181-8a16-4578-b5e9-8e8d87ad8b06\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8727079a-faa4-40bf-83e6-a5e0e01288f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-23f83372-57da-459f-8d59-492cdd5165b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-71218716-5c01-4a7a-babe-433fee9ff098\" style=\"color:#555555;\">PQC의 손끝 미세조정에 따라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc4d5ca6-a86d-4e1c-9e4d-1332da674997\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2c1d8f2-1312-4a39-9e9e-6ce4377d8af0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상의 편차는 심하게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ad4b57a7-e0b7-475c-9ac4-c3c624364348\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1961349c-4020-4693-8697-74ede3d78150\" style=\"color:#555555;\">차이가 날 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><