"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-07e10804-62f3-48ef-85af-b95bac5b7d21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e0326f18-6759-4fbb-aed2-fb94b16d8436\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d722a46-79be-4490-9b56-b549b9e09fda\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">그렇기 때문에 반드시 본 작업 전에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-29c1634d-0fea-45cc-9fe9-5723bd96b85e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd6398fd-edec-4bb9-b249-a1db3ab7a8fb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">샘플을 만드실 것을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f123dfa3-d97a-421f-87ab-08481d61e1e6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3f8e927-3cec-4d6e-9dd4-427874bf654a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c7b397af-b474-4dda-a8d0-b1b4c274f29c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be3560d5-cc59-4f44-baaf-24cc3908bcfe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 고객 여러분이 아시겠지만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-68f03480-fff6-4ac6-807b-8c9b4c361ac3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ec39dbc-1635-4e5f-8cd1-964f66e59c2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 인쇄와 오프셋인쇄는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4a310d9e-edb1-41a4-94e2-88cf6577863c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-516a6d1e-72e2-45dd-ac4c-c37c901280aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">근본적으로 방식이 달라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d1a22a12-0deb-4ac7-958a-ea7002158463\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-078fb8fb-016f-49cc-93e8-8736e42642b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상 편차가 큽니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-eb475b5e-4953-483c-be0a-d3b2f3141e50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75d79d1b-03a0-4c2f-af65-cd2236299a1a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d3b9e322-e920-4fad-9596-4bb44bdad4b4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d80b38e3-4849-4add-b87b-29bebb45daaf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 디지털이라도 반드시</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1b1331ab-e9ce-444c-a63a-9098fa440496\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7cc74e52-8b7e-40c2-b94b-aadd3069f1e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시험인쇄를 해서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3c2f1e05-945d-4e88-8f7a-d46dbdcda7bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0524de5f-d359-4feb-9182-95e356f62478\" style=\"color:#555555;\">교정이나 오타 또는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-baac0680-3ca2-40ca-8884-353700de233d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c5c584f-2369-448a-a44f-1c1ed4bcbb95\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색감의 형성을 체크하실 것을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dd97466e-e303-4414-b44a-2d5d671e02c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-474123be-698f-4d62-9642-2b5cbe768c64\" style=\"color:#555555;\">추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d75f7c5d-3896-4914-9f2d-cc50ccd4035e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223767825242/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac2b7169-5ed7-4364-9b01-d7ca2c7a9349\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-68982e5e-6dba-40dd-80a3-36bc44119b52\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8e58379b-786e-4a25-85f5-160c9d1913a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>셋, 패키지 전문 디자인 회사에 디자인을 의뢰하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fefefa6d-3d82-42f4-8262-8f948e23a754\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-67bbb186-6319-4ab6-8dba-60af2dc692e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-80f2f9b2-3c8c-4c90-b68f-8e54754bc6b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-982d9322-9a5e-43a3-aeec-d346ce452062\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지 인쇄는 디자인이 생명입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-032917b5-f9c2-4b63-8b28-fe7819dc71ea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df8a7cd1-1f8e-4c8b-a111-df5d4636cf07\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그런 중에도 패키지는 심플함과</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-be445689-34dc-4464-83e5-49ac0f11c866\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77c930c9-fe25-4125-b582-aae9c158a32e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 제품의 특성을 잘 살릴 수 있는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c10ac939-d4e9-4c20-b0aa-d5e8641f4405\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cdf5a904-b9b8-441a-b481-b880bd74ad00\" style=\"color:#555555;\">직관성이 가장 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4581987b-65a2-41cc-98eb-d1558f5a4ad9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4b5c577-a3c2-4cfd-b28f-0cffff03d52b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7318b00e-9710-4160-a5a3-ad1c43440c6d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fa60a5a2-23ea-4d25-9562-fd3881167b5a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 전문화된</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-67c94cae-d941-4db1-8614-625ee78aab23\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa689360-f950-4e94-a2b2-03a15f08efe2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">디자인 인력이 디자인에서부터</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-73919b5e-3e84-4587-b1e3-a938d94e6457\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e79f14fe-b305-4583-b087-ac497869a27e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">견적, 고객 대응, 감리, 제작, 납품까지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc996c8b-e5d6-4ddc-aeab-3306278dbe10\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d405c85f-e182-4b57-bf4a-49481b60231b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">모든 부분을 고객과 함께 하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5bd160b2-91eb-428a-82df-664b7feef84c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4288d09-d5d8-45a6-a49c-48947c24a35b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0f9db15d-af32-4119-a86a-d06834e4e015\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0049ace6-c7e7-4168-b8a1-05ceef8a1337\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>고객과 함께 성장하고 싶은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-07dfa54f-924c-42ec-b278-f067277e8315\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-82ad2717-b90a-4852-bbd6-023337d84302\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니에게</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b4ec01a6-2aa4-4122-8a99-0ceef6c030d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-80d6c9a6-d07f-4803-8ccd-202558d85c5b\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>지금 바로 전화 주세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-fe343a90-f807-4374-b256-cd3cb4509997\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db84a323-e2f3-45a8-adae-82b5bf64af88\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3a775ca3-5397-4f91-ad5c-29625a324d45\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>제작 시 실패하지 않는 방법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-94105715-a845-4260-a7d2-17cbe130fabb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-137aee29-01bc-493d-81f2-d01b387d8008\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f7aff22-6b45-4ecc-a218-d48a671ec038\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>1. 반드시 비교견적을 진행하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-149573c1-e010-4fae-b104-40753dedfc4f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3fcfa5b7-00b9-4e61-8de4-07c1208a1d52\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 비교견적 시에 단가만을 비교하시는 바보 같은(?) 판단은 하지 마시기 바랍니다. 패키지는 결국 브랜드파워이고 마케팅의 수단입니다. 그렇기 때문에 단가의 약간의 차이를 가지고 업체를 선정하는 것은 결코 바람직하지 않습니다. 누가 얼마나 적극적으로 대응해 주고 또는 잘 모르는 부분을 이해가 쉽도록 설명하는 업체를 선정하시는 것이 결국은 도움이 되실 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-150e46a9-5233-4e96-8cb6-76dd7b01107d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6d38d5b0-36e0-40e1-a0f1-1b68dfac7030\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93443fb6-a954-4fd2-a859-cdba69320bfb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eba7a70b-dd76-4710-87a1-d60a424c52a9\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>2. 가격뿐 아니라 납기와 포트폴리오를 반드시 확인하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-286427f0-09aa-41f7-b5d2-922f8bab04a2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ccededa-376f-486c-9e86-cd4e05b7e73d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지는 납기가 중요합니다. 심하게 날 때는 몇 주가 차이 날 때가 있습니다. 반드시 납기를 확인하시고 발주하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8630f9ef-cfa9-4b61-984e-eed2ab5fc51f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-71a7c223-a056-4c35-9831-d0d9f35d8fee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-034ea8f8-bc20-4a10-b9ae-564651f8b2ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-20a2a88d-3a65-4512-b68d-39f37c0f8087\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>3. 샘플 제작이 가능한 업체를 선정하는 것이 유리합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3eeba030-2514-4785-9200-5ea00f600d92\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-596019de-37e5-422c-9f09-66fc936a7d17\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 샘플 제작이 안되는 사이즈나 형태가 있기는 하지만 작은 용기의 화장품의 경우 거의 대부분 샘플 제작이 가능합니다. 반드시 본 작업 전에 샘플을 만들고 확인하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50d21704-cad1-447c-8424-a7b93ed9bd29\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ec8130d-088b-4d3f-9aff-f30bd75a2dc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a067c3af-39b4-4107-b586-df60137861b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223767825242/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223767825242#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}